data.description: Darling home surrounded by towering trees, was remodeled in 2022 with upgraded black quartz counters, cabinets and appliances in kitchen; new lighting and luxury vinyl flooring throughout. Electrical wiring replaced in kitchen, and all faucets and much of plumbing replaced in baths and kitchen.  Storage spaces and spacious closets throughout the house. The roof was replaced in 2022. Outside, a covered patio looks out on a sizable back yard surrounded by an 8 ft. wooden fence for complete privacy. Outside of that fence is a large pasture, which could serve as a haven for pets, a huge garden, or to build a guest house or workshop. Single garage is over-sized providing additional storage. Buyer and buyer's agent to confirm all facts and check with local authorities on the possibilities of use or development of pasture, as well as confirm all facts relating to this property, including but not limited to, measurements, schools, utility service.
